Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Drug addiction spreading
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xqb5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Jul 1986
Mrs Reagan's 'Say no to drugs' campaign isn't enough to tackle the growing social problem of addiction. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less